Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it'd start pouring like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do if someone wanted to use the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there's no fitting a third person in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already a tight squeeze as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all wet, Jun'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.60,0:00:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.23,0:00:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes it is! It's winter right now, you'll\Ncatch a cold if you're not careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There, you should be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:01:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, forget what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me wipe you off this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.95,0:01:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.91,0:01:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Imagine if someone were to see us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be even worse if it was someone we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.99,0:01:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The glass is fogging over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been with you all this time, yet \Nwe've never made any memories like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be making a lot of new memories from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you feel how my heart is racing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I sure can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine's also going a mile a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been chilly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
